Andr=E9s Villaveces
Bridging a gap between Physics and Logic: the role of Sheaves

Ralf Kr=F6mer
  =46rom Cantor to Sheaves. The development of the concepts of direct and
inverse limits =96 a case study on shifts in mathematical methodology =20=

in the
prehistory of Category Theory

